column1: Thanks for the reply! "Options nearer to ATM have higher intrinsic" - do you mean extrinsic instead? ATM should be 0 intrinsic. But I do understand your explanation for why the extrinsic value has to be the same for put/call at some strike K, because otherwise there's an arbitrage opportunity!
